Class Student

java.lang.Object
Student
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Comparable<java.lang.Object>
Direct Known Subclasses:
Instate, International, Outstate
public abstract class Student
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<java.lang.Object>
This is an abstract class which includes an abstract method called tuition due that its subclasses inherit. This class also includes the compareto method in order to compare the first name and the last name of a student.
